ANNOTATION
for final qualification work student ___________________________________
on a subject: «Features of formation of a management team and assessment of its efficiency»

Keywords in work: team, management team, team approach, management, efficiency.

In final qualification work the concept of formation of effective team in management of the modern organization is considered.
Relevance of a subject of research is caused by need of finding of system decisions on formation of effective management teams for the real mode of time. 
Research objective: providing own approach to formation and assessment of efficiency of a management team.
Object of research: organizational and administrative process of formation and use of management teams in various spheres, search of ways of increase of efficiency of their activity is.
Object of research: organizational and theoretical and prakseologichesky problems of features of activity of effective management teams.
Final qualification work consists of introduction, three heads, the conclusion, the list used sources and applications. Relevance of the chosen subject locates in introduction, the purpose, research problems are formed, the characteristic of the practical importance of work is given.
In chapter 1 theoretical aspects of formation of effective team in management of the modern organization are opened. The concept "team" is considered, advantages, shortcomings and consequences of team approach are defined; process of formation of an effective management team is investigated; basic principles of an effective management team; the analysis of the factors influencing success of creation of a solid management team is carried out.
Chapter 2 is devoted to detection of features of creation of a management team on the example of Sibirsky delikates Group.
In the head the principles and techniques of formation of management teams on the example of the enterprises RK "Oaklets", "Dairy Business", are investigated by Rusagro Group. The general characteristic is given and the analysis of problems of creation of team of management of Sibirsky delikates Group is carried out.
In the third lava of this work offers on detection of features of formation of a management team are developed, the assessment of its efficiency is given.
The conducted research allowed the author to formulate the following conclusions:
1) Team building is a process of purposeful formation of a special method of the interaction of people in the organization allowing is effective to realize their power intellectual and creative potentials.
2) The effective team — is the group created in the special way specially picked up both on professional, and on personal features of people.
3) The presented analysis of the enterprises illustrated methods of formation of management teams, both in system of public authorities, and in a business environment. In the analysis the companies which used the scientific techniques of formation of management teams and the companies using the author's approaches were used. All companies work during the present period of time and methods of formation and an assessment of management teams are used and now. The companies are presented in the different markets of real sector of economy that allows to draw the generalized conclusions for all business of the sphere.
4) The management team is the collective which is carefully created, well operated, self-organizing, quickly and effectively reacting to any changes of a market situation, solving all problems as a unit.
The management team consists of group of the experts belonging to various spheres of organizational activity and working in common on the solution of these or those problems.
The management team acts as a peculiar backbone element which accumulates needs of all members of the organization; unites and allocates the general requirements of the organization; forms the purposes which achievement allows to satisfy these requirements; develops mechanisms of their achievement and will organize activity of all members of the organization.
5) The main call of the present for business — alternation of generations and alternation of generations of management can be overcome due to application of through techniques of selection of candidates. To concentrate at a stage of selection of profile managers, but not to treat then for diseases all collective. Developing the author's programs of selection of candidates, applying scientific approaches. On the basis of the applied techniques of formation of management teams it is possible to reveal correlation of teams with the reached economic results.
In the conclusion the results of the conducted research are summed up. 
Final qualification work contains 10 tables and 10 drawings.

